name: In re TRANSFER OF ATTORNEY TO INACTIVE STATUS PURSUANT TO Pa.R.D.E. 219(k)(1)
name_abbreviation: In re Transfer of Attorney to Inactive Status Pursuant to Pa.R.D.E. 219(k)(1)

parties: In re TRANSFER OF ATTORNEY TO INACTIVE STATUS PURSUANT TO Pa.R.D.E. 219(k)(l).

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM:
AND NOW, this 22nd day of July, 1998, it is ORDERED that OSCAR GASKINS is hereby transferred to inactive status as a member of the Bar of this Commonwealth, pursuant to Pa.R.D.E. 219(k)(l).
opinions.author: PER CURIAM:
